beer.beer_description: Somewhat of a companion beer to Red Sky, White Sky is an amped up witbier (Belgian white ale) infused with jasmine and chamomile flowers, as well as the classic witbier botanicals of coriander and sweet orange peel and then dry hopped with Galaxy and Mosaic hops.
